<p>2 - As we are using Docker, the initial setup is very simple. We are going to use a Vault image, which you can find the source <a href="https://github.com/cgswong/docker-vault">here</a>. Put the following content in your <code class="highlighter-rouge">docker-compose.yml</code></p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
