<p>Now before anything else, you should save the unseal keys that you got during the last step, (as without them you canâ€™t store or retrieve any key), and make sure to store it in a safe place where no one can access it and that you wonâ€™t lose for any reason. If you need to send them to an organizational partner you can use <a href="https://www.bovedahq.com/">Boveda</a>.</p>

<p>At this point you should have Vault up and running. Letâ€™s check itâ€™s status. In your browser make sure to replace for your server: <code class="highlighter-rouge">http://yourserver:8200/v1/seal-status</code></p>

<p>You should see the response:</p>

